Summary: Orb passed over house heading south-southeast and dropped two other orbs.
divs: Sighting DetailsI was sitting in my bedroom at my computer, at about 10Pm on or about Sept. 26, 2011 when a thought occured to me that I needed to go outside at that moment and look up at the sky to the south. I went outside and witnessed an orange Orb, about 400 feet in the air passing over the neighborhood and heading slowly, silently in a south-southwesterly direction. The orb was approx. 50 in diameter and was translucent. As it passed over the city it dropped two other, smaller orbs and then all three moved out of sight range. They were very beautiful and since I expected to see something up in the sky, I watched them drift off into the night sky, wondering when I might have a chance to see them again.
